   	        <h1 class="marginT20 main-heading-innerPages text-left">Delivery & Shipping Policies</h1>
            	        <p> <strong>Appeti.in </strong>is committed to delivering your 							order in the best possible way. We try our hardest to ensure that 							we provide the most efficient dispatch and for the same we have 							partnered with the best Logistics Service Providers that gets 							your orders to you as swiftly as possible. </p>
                        <p>&nbsp; </p>
                        <p><strong><u>Payment Options</u></strong></p>
            <p>We accept payments made using credit card, debit card and 							net banking. We accept most major Credit/Debit Cards. Pay as you 							like!</p>
                        <p>&nbsp; </p>
                        <p><strong><u>Delivery Area and Timings</u></strong></p>
                        <p>We deliver pan-India in 1-7 business days depending upon 							customer's location. Public Holidays and Saturdays/Sundays are 							excluded from business days since we do not ship anything on 							these days to prevent the lag in shipments.</p>
                        <p>Please note that the delivery timing depends on a number of 							factors like: weather, unforeseen events, traffic conditions and 							other special events. However, we will always endeavour to 							complete the delivery as early as possible and keep you updated 							in case of any changes</p>
                        <p>&nbsp;</p>
                        <p><strong><u>Delivery Charges/Minimum Order</u></strong></p>
            <p>Our all prices are inclusive of all taxes, packaging and 							shipping cost. There are no hidden charges for delivery.</p>
                        <p>&nbsp; </p>
                        <p><strong><u>What if the product is received in 									damaged condition?</u></strong></p>
                        <p>In case of complaints regarding foods that come with a 							warranty from Brand Owners, please refer the issue to the 							concerned Brand Owner. Let us know; we'll help you regarding the 							same.</p>
                        <p> If you think, you have received the food items in a bad condition 							or if the packaging is tampered with or damaged before 							delivery, please email us at <strong><a href="mailto:contact@appeti.in">contact@appeti.in</a></strong> mentioning 							your Order ID within 24 hours of accepting the package. We will 							request you for the pictures of the shipment and individual 							pictures of the boxes which will be provided to the Food Vendors 							and the courier partner within 48 hours of shipment delivery. If 							the claim is genuine as found by us, the Food Vendor and the 							Courier Partner, <strong>we will get the shipment 								picked back and initiate exchange or refund for the same.</strong></p>
